---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/base.astro'
import AI from '../components/AI.astro';
import Services from '../components/Services.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
	title="fffood / What we do" 
	description="How much does it cost"
	hero="/img/heroes/crew.jpg"
	heroModifier="hero--slim"
	showCTA={true}>


	<section class="section section--darkest">
		<div class="section__inner">
			<h1>What we do</h1>	
			<p class="u-measure"><strong>We help small businesses and growing brands show up with clarity and confidence</strong> — online and off. Whether you need a joined-up digital presence, a refreshed brand, or a better way of working behind the scenes, we'll help you figure out what matters and deliver it without the faff.</p>	
		</div> <!-- /.section__inner -->
	</section> <!-- /.section -->

	<section class="section section--bubblegum">
		<div class="section__inner">
			
				<h2>Our Process</h2>

				<p class="u-measure"><strong>We follow the same core process for every client</strong> — whether you're a startup, a family business, or an established brand doing a refresh.</p>

				<div class="grid grid--thirds">
					<div class="well well--bubblegum u-shadow">
						<h3 class="u-no-bottom"><span class="u-grey">1.</span> Understand</h3>
						<p>We start with a deep dive into your business — your goals, your audience, and what’s getting in the way. This empathy-led phase is all about clarity.</p>
						<p><em>Output: A strategic plan shaped around your budget, goals and capacity.</em></p>
					</div>

					<div class="well well--bubblegum u-shadow">
						<h3 class="u-no-bottom"><span class="u-grey">2.</span> Plan</h3>				
						<p>Once we understand the challenge, we recommend the right mix of services — from branding and websites to SEO, email, or CRM. Everything has a purpose <a href="/pricing">and a fixed cost</a>.</p>
						<p><em>Output: A focused proposal with all the building blocks, ready to go.</em></p>
					</div>

					<div class="well well--bubblegum u-shadow">
						<h3 class="u-no-bottom"><span class="u-grey">3.</span> Deliver</h3>			
						<p>We build, configure and launch your new assets — whether that's a brand identity, a website, a content pack or a workspace setup. We also offer training so you can run things confidently.</p>
						<p><em>Output: A consistent, professional presence that's built to last.</em></p>
					</div>
				</div>

		</div> <!-- /.section__inner -->
	</section> <!-- /.section -->
	
	<section class="section section--fade">
		<div class="section__inner">
			<h2>What we can help with</h2>
			<p>Here's a flavour of the services we offer — always tailored to your business:</p>
			<Services />
			<p><a class="button button--bubblegum u-top-margin" href="/case-studies">Case studies</a></p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<AI />

</BaseLayout>